        <h1 class="l-hero-h1" style="min-height:auto;line-height:1.25;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:6px 0 14px;font-size:30px">New project. New hire. New partner. New strategy. New focus. New expectations. <em style="color:#93C5FD;font-style:normal">Start with a Ground.</em></h1>
        <p style="font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.82);font-weight:500;line-height:1.65;margin:0 auto 20px;max-width:540px">Groundwork gives everyone a shared understanding from the beginning and keeps it alive as work progresses.</p>
