          <p style="font-size:15px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:24px">Not the organisation. Not the platform. The person. Each account is private until everyone chooses to open the report together. That is what makes honesty possible, and what makes every other capability in the product work.</p>
