      <p class="l-sec-p" style="margin:0 auto 40px;text-align:center;max-width:520px">Founders, managers, people teams, and partners use Groundwork to build a contribution record from the start, not the night before a hard conversation. Everyone checks in independently. The report shows each version at the same time.</p>
