<!-- ABOUT -->
<div id="lp-about" style="display:none">
  <div class="l-wrap-sm">
    <p class="l-sec-label">About</p>
    <h2 class="l-sec-h2">Built by people who kept running into the same problem.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;margin-bottom:40px">
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#4A5568;line-height:1.8">Groundwork was created by people who built and ran companies and kept hitting the same wall. Not open conflict. Quiet misalignment. Different expectations, different assumptions, different ideas of what success looked like, none of it said out loud until it had already become expensive.</p>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#4A5568;line-height:1.8">Real contribution went unseen. Real disagreements went unnamed. Because there was no place for each person to put down their own account and see where it actually matched everyone else's.</p>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#4A5568;line-height:1.8">Groundwork was built to be that place. Each person gives their own account. The report shows where they agree and where they don't. Nobody has to argue their version. The record does it.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="border-left:3px solid #0C447C;padding:20px 20px;background:#EEF4FB;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin-bottom:36px">
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0C447C;margin-bottom:8px">The founding principle</h3>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:#1A1916;line-height:1.75;font-style:italic">The record belongs to the people who built it. Not the organisation. Not the platform. The person. Take that away and people stop being honest. Keep it and everything else works.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:36px">
      <div style="padding:20px;background:#F5F3EF;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #E2E0DB">
        <h3 style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1916;margin-bottom:6px">The product</h3>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.6">A private check-in for each person. One shared report. For two people or twenty.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:20px;background:#F5F3EF;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #E2E0DB">
        <h3 style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1916;margin-bottom:6px">The company</h3>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.6">Groundwork is an independent product. We built it because the tools that existed either captured one side of the picture or required everyone to be in the same room.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;margin-bottom:36px">
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#4A5568;line-height:1.8">Built for the moments that matter most. Something starting. Someone stepping up. A team that needs to see the same picture again.</p>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#4A5568;line-height:1.8">Built for founders, managers, partners, and teams who would rather get aligned early than manage the fallout later.</p>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:#4A5568;line-height:1.8">Built first for African leaders and the companies they run, and useful anywhere people start things together.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:36px">
      <div style="padding:20px;background:#F5F3EF;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #E2E0DB">
        <h3 style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#1A1916;margin-bottom:6px">Our headquarters</h3>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:#6B6560;line-height:1.6">Groundwork<br>9 Wendy Court, David Osieli Road<br>Westlands, Nairobi, Kenya</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center">
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#9B9590;margin-bottom:10px">Questions or feedback</p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@myground.work" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0C447C;text-decoration:none">hello@myground.work</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

